title: Safely Reopening Commercial Real Estate
itunes:title: Safely Reopening Commercial Real Estate
description:
Kent Swig, President at Swig Equities, discusses safely reopening commercial real estate. Swig also points out the importance of national leadership during the pandemic.

Hosts: Carol Massar and Jason Kelly. Producer: Doni Holloway.
